{"tid":1631933,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[18區開花] 一句講晒，聽日一點定八點？","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:37:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T02:58:36.000Z","uid":259319,"like":41,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"35299fdb1d2598f1d8232b6a5abed45d7bae4887","tid":1631933,"uid":259319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:37:52.000Z","msg":"聽日重陽節，根據張圖<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">紅日係下午一點</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我見好多連登仔話<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽晚夜晚八點</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實幾點都好，人多就好辦事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家可有個<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">共識</span></span>，如果一批一點一批八點其實係會分薄咗人手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">八點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span>"},{"pid":"e460fe4ea4f34a6220daff71f75b9cdcce0f661a","tid":1631933,"uid":259319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:38:24.000Z","msg":"會update正負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4a1c9ce1b8ad90355710601ae1623ba85d49c3","tid":1631933,"uid":259319,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:38:57.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到<br />\n請大家幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f77c9b347e8f5144252a0a38a3cfa5f3ab769ee","tid":1631933,"uid":12970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:41:47.000Z","msg":"認真聽日係繼續裝修定點"},{"pid":"aefed5adf30997c526a0455c1ba2293b94a8f832","tid":1631933,"uid":25931