tyle=\"font-size: x-large;\">八點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:45:38.000Z","msg":"可唔可以文宣開花一日<br />\n<br />\n裝修少一日得唔得呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[行動post] 聽日幾點開花？做啲乜嘢好？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632302\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632302</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"182299e3369d44c0323ee60470727cbe769e30cf","tid":1631933,"uid":259319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:45:57.000Z","msg":"1:45am: 21正10負<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a92b1b5868e6e78f4b59afdee2e6ee5818c81ef4","tid":1631933,"uid":247896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:46:28.000Z","msg":"夜晚，快閃後回家<br />\n反正預黨鐵全線封，手足更難走<br />\n不要忘記陣地的教訓"},{"pid":"17e50ef2316c49cc1901939f6c3a71fa41fb4c3f","tid":1631933,"uid":142010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f77c9b347e8f5144252a0a38a3cfa5f3ab769ee","tid":1631933,"uid":12970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:41:47.000Z","msg":"認真聽日係繼續裝修定點"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:53:41.000Z","msg":"對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修<br />\n<br />\n1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX<br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.MEMO紙<br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.善用1823<br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.蟲系魔法師<br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):<br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚<br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢飛個靚髮或者化下妝就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命<br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"b6c9a828423ce999f25195836396909a1fedc082","tid":1631933,"uid":259319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:57:33.000Z","msg":"1:57am: 24正11負<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9358c8af480d1e57faa0bd96b7076a6bc2d4657","tid":1631933,"uid":61334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66e85a88c92ac1327a9cd8d549adff95d5642a9c","tid":1631933,"uid":1544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:48:59.000Z","msg":"一定係一點<br />\n八點咁夜爆到d咩啊 <br />\n手足走又困難<br />\n唔記得太陽落山前先對我地最有利咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:00:12.000Z","msg":"好多人要拜山"},{"pid":"675023822f826e6a8030a259103a28237c315046","tid":1631933,"uid":259319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:01:17.000Z","msg":"2:01am: 25正13負<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02154feaa3f46c2d23e04130993fb99879cdccc0","tid":1631933,"uid":259319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:02:14.000Z","msg":"Sorry原來已經2點<br />\n要休息了 聽日仲要岀嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b1eef66d8d897c7da34a9dafed7df90c150ecf","tid":1631933,"uid":259319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:04:54.000Z","msg":"2:04am: 29個八點，13個一點<img src=\"